docs.text: My name is Stuart Christhilf. I am currently a student at Charlotte Latin School. My passions are Engineering and Computer Science. I graduated from fab academy 2023 and am set to graduate high school in 2025. I plan to double major in electrical engineering and computer science and maybe minor in mechanical engineering or aerospace engineering once I get to colledge.
